lass=\"bb_paragraph\" >You throw wild, unforgettable parties, seduce the city’s elite, and build a harem of exquisite concubines — each woman more dangerous, desirable, and useful than the last. From a brilliant courtesan to a broken slave, a deadly stranger to a foreign princess — every beauty you claim unlocks new inspiration for the grandest events Rome has ever seen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/9b743eaabb740e2f6bd23707b9f64d13.poster.avif?t=1762717920\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/9b743eaabb740e2f6bd23707b9f64d13.webm?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/9b743eaabb740e2f6bd23707b9f64d13.mp4?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But beware: in a world of sex, politics, and betrayal, your greatest weakness might lie in the very arms that please you most.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🔥 Key Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/273512721a8d191c8ac3ac4a2f32cb73.avif?t=1762717920\" width=600 height=559 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/c46e42e47f96d069702f4e465792813a.poster.avif?t=1762717920\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/c46e42e47f96d069702f4e465792813a.webm?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/c46e42e47f96d069702f4e465792813a.mp4?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Empire of Lust</strong>🏛   is a visual novel for adults who crave power, intrigue, and unapologetic pleasure — set against the backdrop of a world where indulgence isn't a sin… it’s a strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/78d92bd77ad1644cd9af2511e989ba63.avif?t=1762717920\" width=600 height=388 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Empire of Lust</strong> 🏛  — Power. Pleasure. Rome.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the heart of Ancient Rome, influence is everything — and no one knows how to climb the social ladder quite like you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/6527a7984a757a9d43b55113e16e3583.poster.avif?t=1762717920\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/6527a7984a757a9d43b55113e16e3583.webm?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3684700/extras/6527a7984a757a9d43b55113e16e3583.mp4?t=1762717920\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span c